# CCA-Audit self-installs its agents and commands into .claude/ when this repo is
# the audit target, and audit runs write trails to .claude/audits/. None of that
# belongs in the repo -- without this line an agent running `git add -A` commits a
# self-install of all 13 agents.
.claude/
